nturies, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.'),(258,84,'_english_answer','field_552c344913294'),(259,84,'section',''),(260,84,'_section','field_552c330c4622f'),(264,54,'rule','a:5:{s:5:\"param\";s:9:\"post_type\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:4:\"faqs\";s:8:\"order_no\";i:0;s:8:\"group_no\";i:0;}'),(265,35,'rule','a:5:{s:5:\"param\";s:9:\"post_type\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:4:\"post\";s:8:\"order_no\";i:0;s:8:\"group_no\";i:0;}'),(266,35,'rule','a:5:{s:5:\"param\";s:9:\"post_type\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:8:\"services\";s:8:\"order_no\";i:0;s:8:\"group_no\";i:1;}'),(267,35,'rule','a:5:{s:5:\"param\";s:9:\"post_type\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:6:\"events\";s:8:\"order_no\";i:0;s:8:\"group_no\";i:2;}'),(268,35,'rule','a:5:{s:5:\"param\";s:9:\"post_type\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:10:\"equipments\";s:8:\"order_no\";i:0;s:8:\"group_no\";i:3;}'),(269,35,'rule','a:5:{s:5:\"param\";s:9:\"post_type\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:4:\"faqs\";s:8:\"order_no\";i:0;s:8:\"group_no\";i:4;}'),(270,70,'_wp_old_slug','auto-draft'),(271,70,'english-title','What types of samples can be tested in the flow cytometer?'),(272,70,'_english-title','field_5501d1e0ba3d9'),(273,70,'english-content','Any single cell or particle suspension can be analyzed, including mammalian cells, bacteria, fungi, dissociated tissue and polystyrene beads. If its cells or particles in suspension are not isolated, they cannot be used in Flow Cytometry.'),(274,70,'_english-content','field_5501d641a0ad1'),(275,84,'english-title','What is a good question for a FAQ?'),(276,84,'_english-title','field_5501d1e0ba3d9'),(277,84,'english-content','<strong>Lorem Ipsum</stro