eference cell, which require 280μL of filled volume. The reference is always distilled and deaerated water. The autosampler requires at least 400μL of sample collected from a well plate, to ensure that the sample cell is completely filled, since the titration syringe needs 120 μL of titrant, however, this volume is performed in multiple small injections quantities totaling just 40μL of titrant injected into the sample cell. Although the sample cell are resistant, use to acidific solutions should be avoided.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe software used in this equipment is MicroCal Origin and iTC<sub>200</sub>.'),(413,112,'_english-content','field_5501d641a0ad1'),(414,112,'image','113'),(415,112,'_image','field_55525b8b4a9d2'),(416,114,'_edit_last','1'),(417,114,'_edit_lock','1431545908:1'),(418,115,'_wp_attached_file','2015/05/DH600426005.jpg'),(419,115,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:4:{s:5:\"width\";i:400;s:6:\"height\";i:400;s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"2015/05/DH600426005.jpg\";s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(420,114,'english-title','HP ML350t06 Computers'),(421,114,'_english-title','field_5501d1e0ba3d9'),(422,114,'english-content','The LaCTAD Bioinformatics is equipped with 3 ML350t06 HP computers, consisting of  two six-core processors (Intel Xeon X5650 2.66GHz 12MB 95W), 128 GB memory (16 HP 8GB 2Rx4)and 05 HP 2TB 3G SATA disks (7.2K 3.5in MDL HDD).'),(423,114,'_english-content','field_5501d641a0ad1'),(424,114,'image','115'),(425,114,'_image','field_55525b8b4a9d2'),(426,117,'_wp_attached_file','2015/05/c02239508.png'),(427,117,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:4:{s:5:\"width\";i:573;s:6:\"height\";i:430;s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"2015/05/c02239508.png\";s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s